<center><font size=7><b>Kat Trap</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 3</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><table border="0">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>DESCRIPTION</B></U></TD>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>POKE(s)</B></U></TD>
</TR>
<tr><td>Multi-POKE</td><td>31039,45</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lives = x</td><td>29362,x (x= 1-128)</td></tr>
<tr><td>See End Screen</td><td>31040,0</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><BR><B>Change x to whatever value you wish, using the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI
<BR><BR>The "Multi-POKE" gives you Infinite Lives and Grenades.
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/YourSinclair/Issue40/Tape/">this issue of Pokes</a> in the alphabetical section.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Your Sinclair issue 40)</i> 

<br><hr>
This hack is for the original version released in 1987.
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<pre>
 10 LET t=0: FOR f=3e4 TO 30016: READ a
 20 POKE f,a: LET t=t+(f- 29990)*a: NEXT f
 30 READ a: IF t<>a THEN STOP
 40 RANDOMIZE USR 3e4
 50 DATA 205,86,5,221,33
 60 DATA 215,253,17,0,1
 70 DATA 62,255,55,205,86
 80 DATA 5,201,33907
 90 POKE 65136,220: POKE 65137,255
100 LET t=0: FOR f=65500 TO 65507
110 READ a: POKE f,a
120 LET t=t+(f- 65490)*a: NEXT f
130 READ a: IF t<>a THEN STOP
140 RANDOMIZE USR 65024
150 DATA&nbsp;62,45,50,63,121,195,0,108,8989: REM for infinite lives
150 DATA 62,1iv,50,178,114,195,0,108,9891: REM for x lives
</pre>
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Also need this line if using x lives:
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;125 LET t=t- (11~liv)
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
</table></center><P>
